        "description": "This data comes from a panel of 4360 observations from 1980 to 1987. It includes information about a worker's type of job, residence area, hourly wage, and so on.\n\n\n=== About this file ===\n\nAbout this file\nInformation about workers, their wage and other relevant features\n\n\n=== Columns & descriptions ===\n\nrownames: [no description]\nnr: identifier\nyear: [no description]\nschool: years of schooling\nexper: years of experience (=age-6-school)\nunion: wage set by collective bargaining?\nethn: ethnicity (black, hisp, other)\nmaried: married?\nhealth: health issues?\nwage: Log of hourly wage\nindustry: a factor with 12 levels\noccupation: a factor with 9 levels\nresidence: a factor with levels (rural area, north east, northern central, south)\n",
